'''''A New Concordance of the Bible''''' (full title '''''A New Concordance of the Bible: Thesaurus of the Language of the Bible, Hebrew and Aramaic, Roots, Words, Proper Names Phrases and Synonyms''''') by [[Avraham Even-Shoshan]] is a [[concordance (publishing)|concordance]] of the [[Hebrew language|Hebrew]] text of the [[Hebrew Bible]], first published in 1977. The [[source text]] used is that of the [[Koren Publishers Jerusalem|Koren]] edition of 1958.

